Data Preview Sampling
In CRM Analytics, use data preview sampling to see a more accurate picture of your data at each node in Preview.
Select Filtered Rows to isolate specific values. Select All Column Values to populate a sample when you need to see all column values.
Nodes such as joins, filters, and transforms apply their logic to the sample data.
Under Data Preview Sampling, select a Sample Size and Sampling Mode.
Click Apply.
title: Understanding Data Preview Sampling in CRM Analytics
